    "88512770": {
      "title": "Nonparametric estimate of spectral density functions of sample covariance matrices: A first step",
      "abstract": "The density function of the limiting spectral distribution of general sample covariance matrices is usually unknown. We propose to use kernel estimators which are proved to be consistent. A simulation study is also conducted to show the performance of the estimators."
